{
  "stem": "14251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the people had been buried in scarcely a foot and a half of dirt with no lime thrown on it or anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by the time we got there, if you got a little cut anywhere and you and the dirt connected, you got the disease, which I got and others did too, but I only had it on my legs.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It couldn't be transferred from person to person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think it's called hoof-and-mouth disease.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it left huge scars where there would just be a hole in your flesh.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There would be no bleeding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could look right down to your bone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother traded in desperation some-- a ring that she still had for potassium permanganate crystals that we would dilute carefully two crystals at a time and use it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Tear some bedding apart, which you had no way to keep clean anyway, and wrap those around, because the flies liked to sit on there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That I remember real well because I had so many of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it took-- it must have taken something like a year and a half for those to heal up on their own.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that occurred because I fell on my knee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- we went in and out of a window in one of those houses, because there was so much typhus that had broken out among this German population.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Anyway, we were in some camps, here, there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother dug her way out of-- with a spoon so we could get away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then we somehow-- I remember riding on a-- on a cart.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That always means horse and cart, nothing motorized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the Italians had hidden us under-- there were also Italian prisoners of war there, men.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
